Hello! I'd be happy to help you with your question.

As we were just discussing Akash's work at THE Rubixcon, I noticed that he mentioned developing a deep understanding of the Software Development Life Cycle (SDLC). Can you tell me more about what he means by this? How did he contribute to each stage of the SDLC during his time there?

Also, I saw that Akash designed and developed a scalable dynamicScan QR code and analytics platform. What specific features or functionalities does this project entail?
